import React, { useState } from 'react'; import { Shield, Search, Package, AlertCircle, Eye, AlertTriangle } from 'lucide-react'; const ReturnAnomalyPage = () => { const [selectedAlert, setSelectedAlert] = useState(null); const [riskLevelFilter, setRiskLevelFilter] = useState('All'); const returnAnomalies = [ { id: 'RA001', customerId: 'C987654321', pattern: 'High-value return abuse', returnCount: 12, timeframe: '30 days', totalValue: '$4,567.89', riskScore: 94, category: 'Serial Returner', title: 'High-value return abuse', riskLevel: 'High', description: 'Customer initiated 12 returns in 30 days', investigationBrief: 'Analysis shows consistent pattern of returns within 24-48 hours of purchase, primarily on electronics and designer items. Payment methods vary but shipping addresses remain consistent.', riskIndicators: ['high_value_returns', 'short_ownership_period', 'multiple_categories', 'frequent_returns'], subAgentResults: { behaviorAnalysis: { score: 89, confidence: 'High' }, paymentAnalysis: { score: 72, confidence: 'Medium' }, addressVerification: { score: 95, confidence: 'High' }, deviceFingerprinting: { score: 83, confidence: 'High' } } }, { id: 'RA002', customerId: 'C456789012', pattern: 'Cross-category return pattern', returnCount: 8, timeframe: '14 days', totalValue: '$1,234.56', riskScore: 76, category: 'Suspicious Pattern', title: 'Cross-category return pattern', riskLevel: 'Medium', description: 'Multiple returns across different product categories in short timeframe', investigationBrief: 'Customer has returned items from electronics, clothing, and home goods categories within a 2-week period. Returns cite various reasons but follow similar timing patterns.', riskIndicators: ['cross_category_returns', 'compressed_timeframe', 'varied_reasons'], subAgentResults: { behaviorAnalysis: { score: 76, confidence: 'Medium' }, paymentAnalysis: { score: 68, confidence: 'Medium' }, addressVerification: { score: 82, confidence: 'High' }, deviceFingerprinting: { score: 71, confidence: 'Medium' } } }, { id: 'RA003', customerId: 'C123456789', pattern: 'Refund timing manipulation', returnCount: 5, timeframe: '7 days', totalValue: '$899.99', riskScore: 45, category: 'Policy Abuse', title: 'Refund timing manipulation', riskLevel: 'Low', description: 'Customer returns items just before warranty expiration', investigationBrief: 'Customer consistently returns items within days of warranty expiration across multiple purchases. Pattern suggests deliberate timing to maximize usage while still qualifying for returns.', riskIndicators: ['warranty_timing', 'consistent_pattern', 'policy_exploitation'], subAgentResults: { behaviorAnalysis: { score: 45, confidence: 'Medium' }, paymentAnalysis: { score: 60, confidence: 'High' }, addressVerification: { score: 88, confidence: 'High' }, deviceFingerprinting: { score: 55, confidence: 'Medium' } } } ]; // Filter anomalies based on selected risk level const filteredAnomalies = returnAnomalies.filter(anomaly => { if (riskLevelFilter === 'All') return true; return anomaly.riskLevel === riskLevelFilter; }); const handleAction = (id, action) => { console.log(`Action taken on ${id}: ${action}`); }; return (

)) ) : (

)}
); }; const InvestigationPanel = ({ selectedAlert, handleAction }) => { const getRiskColor = (riskLevel) => { switch (riskLevel) { case 'High': return 'bg-red-600/90 text-white border-red-400'; case 'Medium': return 'bg-yellow-500/90 text-black border-yellow-400'; case 'Low': return 'bg-green-500/90 text-white border-green-400'; default: return 'bg-neutral-700 text-white border-neutral-600'; } }; return (

); }; export default ReturnAnomalyPage;
